This License describes how all of nederliver's projects may and may not be used. This License is subject to change by nederliver at their sole discretion at any time. This License was last altered on November 12, 2025.

## PERMITTED USES

* You are permitted to use any nederliver's projects for personal, non-commercial use. You may use them in your single-player world and modify them, as long as you do not distribute modified versions of any nederliver's projects.
* You are permitted to use nederliver's projects in their unmodified, full form on your public or private servers. Itâ€™s appreciated, but not required, to leave a note somewhere on your server crediting nederliver.
* You are permitted to use nederliver's projects in their unmodified, full form as part of publicly distributed modpacks. If you do so, you must credit nederliver and include a link to a relevant project.
* You are permitted to create content (e.g., videos, livestreams) covering and showcasing any of nederliver's projects, provided you credit nederliver and include a link to a relevant project.
* You are permitted to distribute addons to nederliver's projects provided they do not include any original code. You must credit nederliver and include a link to a relevant project.

## PROHIBITED USES

* You are prohibited from redistributing or re-uploading any nederliver's projects, modified or unmodified.
* You are prohibited from redistributing individual parts, files, or standalone components of any nederliver's projects.
* You are prohibited from including parts of nederliver's projects in your datapacks or mods.
* You are prohibited from distributing modified versions of nederliver's projects in your modpacks or datapack-packs without nederliver's permission.
* You are forbidden to use any nederliver datapacks in any publicly distributed "datapack-packs" without nederliver's permission. A "datapack-pack" is a collection of datapacks offered for download in bundled form. It is distinct from a modpack because it can be used with an unmodified client.
* You are prohibited from claiming that any of nederliver's projects were made by you.
* You are prohibited to use any nederliver's projects to train artificial intelligence models.
